quizzes.question: Which of the following corresponds to the not equal to operator?
quizzes.textContent:
[h1]Comparison Operators[/h1]

[b]Comparison[/b] operators compare two values (numbers or strings).
Comparison operators are used inside conditional statements, and evaluate to either [b]TRUE[/b] or [b]FALSE[/b]. [img id="2367" width="100%"]
